text: Beerwah, Queensland is a rural town in the Sunshine Coast Region of Queensland, Australia, located about 80 km north of Brisbane. It had a population of 7,734 people as of the 2021 census. == Notable people == *Bob Irwin *Steve Irwin *Bindi Irwin == References == == Other websites == * Category:Australia Category:Towns in Queensland
